Text: Costume Shoppehave been receiving a few calls about where to pick up a costume The address is as follows Costume Shoppe Ave SE It seems that most people are leaving the task of picking out their costume until the last minute Margo has introduced lots of new costumes for this year Hint Hint the later you leave it the bigger the line up at the Costume Shoppe We would really like to encourage all of our Deputies to wear a costume If you have any questions please give me a call at thanks Sheila atthtm

John I hope all is going well I have heard lots of great things about your online system I hope it is going well on your end I just wanted to touch base with you to see how you are doing with the fundraising I find it a very humbling process asking people for money You should hit up Chris at Koch Sheila atthtm
